{"title":"讲演","authors":["天马","方成"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":10,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲演"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗  方成画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载：10月15日，东京的法西斯分子在京桥公会堂举行大讲演会，支持对浅沼的行凶。偌大的一个会场，听众、讲演者和记者合在一起，只有寥寥数人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会场外口号震天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声声：惩办杀人犯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会场内却这么冷冷清清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凄凄惨惨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有那桌儿椅儿干瞪眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢脸！丢脸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似这般尴尬场面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如何作讲演？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腿在发抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心在打颤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这嘴巴压根儿不听使唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望窗外：红旗招展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒潮一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万人民举铁拳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作难！作难！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃奶气力都使尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这车轮儿啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偏偏扭不转！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}